            <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Process</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">8 Steps to Set Up a Family Business in Delhi</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle" style="text-align:left;max-width:100%;">Patron's family business setup pipeline runs from the family business architecture diagnostic through HUF formation (where applicable), family operating entity setup (Pvt Ltd via MCA SPICe+ or LLP via FiLLiP), family constitution drafting via consultative process, private family trust setup under the Indian Trusts Act 1882, succession instruments (wills, shareholders' agreements, powers of attorney), tax and compliance setup under the Income Tax Act 2025 and the family council annual review calendar. Each step is a fixed deliverable - no surprises mid-engagement.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-content">
                    <span class="step-badge">Step 1</span>
                    <h3 class="step-title">Family Business Architecture Diagnostic</h3>
                    <p>60-minute opening session followed by 10-14 day diagnostic mapping current structure, family composition, religion-based vehicle eligibility, business scale and succession-stage conversations status; output is the architecture memo with recommended vehicle combination.</p>
                </div>
